▶ {jang 'avwI'; jIghung je.:sen@@jang:v, 'avwI':n, jI-:v, ghung:v, je:adv}
  "The guard replies: 'I am also hungry.'"

▶ {jatlh qama'; jI'oj.:sen@@jatlh:v, qama':n, jI-:v, 'oj:v}
  "The prisoner says: 'I am thirsty.'"

▶ {jang 'avwI'; jI'oj je.:sen@@jang:v, 'avwI':n, jI-:v, 'oj:v, je:adv}
  "The guard replies: 'I am also thirsty.'"

▶ {jatlh qama'; jIDoy'qu'.:sen@@jatlh:v, qama':n, jI-:v, Doy':v, -qu':v}
  "The prisoner says: 'I am very tired.'"

▶ {jatlh 'avwI'; jIDoy'be'.:sen@@jatlh:v, 'avwI':n, jI-:v, Doy':v, -be':v}
  "The guard says: 'I am not tired.'"
